# Leacme.Recory

**Leacme Recory** is a cross-platform application that is currently targeted for mobile devices. It is build using the [Godot Engine](https://github.com/godotengine/godot).

This application features the ability to record and save a voice message using your device's microphone and play it back.

![][image_screenshot]
![index](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6654513/71703788-db3ef480-2d93-11ea-986d-ba26d071d875.png)

## Application Compiling

The application can be compiled into the platform-specific executable with the Godot Engine via the following [instructions](https://docs.godotengine.org/en/latest/getting_started/workflow/export/index.html). Make sure to run `nuget restore` to fetch dependencies specified in the .csproj file prior to building with Godot.

## Application Usage

Hold the Record button while speaking into the microphone, and hold the Play button to play back the saved message.
